{
    "verses": [
        {
            "id": 6156,
            "verse_number": 10,
            "verse_key": "100:10",
            "hizb_number": 60,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
            "ruku_number": 544,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "وَحُصِّلَ مَا فِى ٱلصُّدُورِ",
            "page_number": 600,
            "juz_number": 30,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96165,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "And that within the breasts is obtained,<sup foot_note=197802>1</sup>"
                },
                {
                    "id": 214998,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Dan dikumpul serta didedahkan segala yang terpendam dalam dada?"
                },
                {
                    "id": 1097133,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "আর অন্তরে যা (কিছু লুকানো) আছে তা প্রকাশ করা হবে,"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 6157,
            "verse_number": 11,
            "verse_key": "100:11",
            "hizb_number": 60,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
            "ruku_number": 544,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "إِنَّ رَبَّهُم بِهِمْ يَوْمَئِذٍ لَّخَبِيرٌۢ",
            "page_number": 600,
            "juz_number": 30,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96166,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "Indeed, their Lord with them, that Day, is [fully] Aware.<sup foot_note=197803>1</sup>"
                },
                {
                    "id": 214862,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Sesungguhnya Tuhan mereka Maha Mengetahui dengan mendalam tentang (balasan yang diberikanNya kepada) mereka - pada hari itu."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1097134,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "নিঃসন্দেহে তাদের প্রতিপালক সেদিন তাদের সম্পর্কে পুরোপুরি অবহিত থাকবেন।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 6158,
            "verse_number": 1,
            "verse_key": "101:1",
            "hizb_number": 60,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
            "ruku_number": 545,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": " ٱلْقَارِعَةُ",
            "page_number": 600,
            "juz_number": 30,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96188,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "The Striking Calamity -"
                },
                {
                    "id": 214644,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Hari yang menggemparkan,"
                },
                {
                    "id": 1097135,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "মহা বিপদ"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 6159,
            "verse_number": 2,
            "verse_key": "101:2",
            "hizb_number": 60,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
            "ruku_number": 545,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "مَا ٱلْقَارِعَةُ",
            "page_number": 600,
            "juz_number": 30,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96193,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "What is the Striking Calamity?"
                },
                {
                    "id": 220438,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Apa dia hari yang menggemparkan itu?"
                },
                {
                    "id": 1097136,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "কী সেই মহা বিপদ?"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 6160,
            "verse_number": 3,
            "verse_key": "101:3",
            "hizb_number": 60,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
            "ruku_number": 545,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "وَمَآ أَدْرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلْقَارِعَةُ",
            "page_number": 600,
            "juz_number": 30,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96195,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "And what can make you know what is the Striking Calamity?"
                },
                {
                    "id": 216623,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Dan apa jalannya engkau dapat mengetahui kedahsyatan hari yang menggemparkan itu? -"
                },
                {
                    "id": 1097137,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "মহা বিপদ সম্পর্কে তুমি কী জান?"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 6161,
            "verse_number": 4,
            "verse_key": "101:4",
            "hizb_number": 60,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
            "ruku_number": 545,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "يَوْمَ يَكُونُ ٱلنَّاسُ كَٱلْفَرَاشِ ٱلْمَبْثُوثِ",
            "page_number": 600,
            "juz_number": 30,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96197,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "It is the Day when people will be like moths, dispersed,<sup foot_note=197804>1</sup>"
                },
                {
                    "id": 216765,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "(Hari itu ialah: hari kiamat), hari manusia menjadi seperti kelkatu yang terbang berkeliaran,"
                },
                {
                    "id": 1097138,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "সে দিন মানুষ হবে বিক্ষিপ্ত পতঙ্গের মত"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 6162,
            "verse_number": 5,
            "verse_key": "101:5",
            "hizb_number": 60,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
            "ruku_number": 545,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "وَتَكُونُ ٱلْجِبَالُ كَٱلْعِهْنِ ٱلْمَنفُوشِ",
            "page_number": 600,
            "juz_number": 30,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96199,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "And the mountains will be like wool, fluffed up.<sup foot_note=197805>1</sup>"
                },
                {
                    "id": 216775,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Dan gunung-ganang menjadi seperti bulu yang dibusar berterbangan."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1097139,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "আর পর্বতগুলো হবে ধুনা রঙ্গিন পশমের মত।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 6163,
            "verse_number": 6,
            "verse_key": "101:6",
            "hizb_number": 60,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
            "ruku_number": 545,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "فَأَمَّا مَن ثَقُلَتْ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ",
            "page_number": 600,
            "juz_number": 30,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96201,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "Then as for one whose scales are heavy [with good deeds],"
                },
                {
                    "id": 216766,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Setelah berlaku demikian, maka (manusia akan diberikan tempatnya menurut amal masing-masing); adapun orang yang berat timbangan amal baiknya, -"
                },
                {
                    "id": 1097140,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "অতঃপর যার (সৎ কর্মের) পাল্লা ভারি হবে।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 6164,
            "verse_number": 7,
            "verse_key": "101:7",
            "hizb_number": 60,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
            "ruku_number": 545,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "فَهُوَ فِى عِيشَةٍ رَّاضِيَةٍ",
            "page_number": 600,
            "juz_number": 30,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96203,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "He will be in a pleasant life."
                },
                {
                    "id": 220432,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Maka ia berada dalam kehidupan yang senang lenang."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1097141,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "সে সুখী জীবন যাপন করবে।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 6165,
            "verse_number": 8,
            "verse_key": "101:8",
            "hizb_number": 60,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
            "ruku_number": 545,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "وَأَمَّا مَنْ خَفَّتْ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ",
            "page_number": 600,
            "juz_number": 30,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96205,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "But as for one whose scales are light,"
                },
                {
                    "id": 216338,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Sebaliknya orang yang ringan timbangan amal baiknya, -"
                },
                {
                    "id": 1097142,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "আর যার (সৎকর্মের) পাল্লা হালকা হবে,"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 6166,
            "verse_number": 9,
            "verse_key": "101:9",
            "hizb_number": 60,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
            "ruku_number": 545,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "فَأُمُّهُۥ هَاوِيَةٌ",
            "page_number": 600,
            "juz_number": 30,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96207,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "His refuge<sup foot_note=197806>1</sup> will be an abyss.<sup foot_note=197807>2</sup>"
                },
                {
                    "id": 217585,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Maka tempat kembalinya ialah \"Haawiyah\""
                },
                {
                    "id": 1097143,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "(জাহান্নামের) অতলস্পর্শী গর্তই হবে তার বাসস্থান।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 6167,
            "verse_number": 10,
            "verse_key": "101:10",
            "hizb_number": 60,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
            "ruku_number": 545,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "وَمَآ أَدْرَىٰكَ مَا هِيَهْ",
            "page_number": 600,
            "juz_number": 30,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96189,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "And what can make you know what that is?"
                },
                {
                    "id": 215661,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Dan apa jalannya engkau dapat mengetahui, apa dia \"Haawiyah\" itu?"
                },
                {
                    "id": 1097144,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "তুমি কি জান তা কী?"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 6168,
            "verse_number": 11,
            "verse_key": "101:11",
            "hizb_number": 60,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
            "ruku_number": 545,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "نَارٌ حَامِيَةٌۢ",
            "page_number": 600,
            "juz_number": 30,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96190,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "It is a Fire, intensely hot."
                },
                {
                    "id": 215670,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "(Haawiyah itu ialah): api yang panas membakar."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1097145,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "জ্বলন্ত আগুন।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 6169,
            "verse_number": 1,
            "verse_key": "102:1",
            "hizb_number": 60,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
            "ruku_number": 546,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": " أَلْهَىٰكُمُ ٱلتَّكَاثُرُ",
            "page_number": 600,
            "juz_number": 30,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96211,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "Competition in [worldly] increase diverts you"
                },
                {
                    "id": 217970,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Kamu telah dilalaikan (daripada mengerjakan amal bakti) oleh perbuatan berlumba-lumba untuk mendapat dengan sebanyak-banyaknya (harta benda, anak-pinak pangkat dan pengaruh), -"
                },
                {
                    "id": 1097146,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "অধিক (পার্থিব) সুখ সম্ভোগ লাভের মোহ তোমাদেরকে (অধিক গুরুত্বপূর্ণ বিষয় হতে) ভুলিয়ে রেখেছে।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 6170,
            "verse_number": 2,
            "verse_key": "102:2",
            "hizb_number": 60,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
            "ruku_number": 546,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "حَتَّىٰ زُرْتُمُ ٱلْمَقَابِرَ",
            "page_number": 600,
            "juz_number": 30,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96213,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "Until you visit the graveyards.<sup foot_note=197808>1</sup>"
                },
                {
                    "id": 214965,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Sehingga kamu masuk kubur."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1097147,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "এমনকি (এ অবস্থাতেই) তোমরা কবরে এসে পড়।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 6171,
            "verse_number": 3,
            "verse_key": "102:3",
            "hizb_number": 60,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
            "ruku_number": 546,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "كَلَّا سَوْفَ تَعْلَمُونَ",
            "page_number": 600,
            "juz_number": 30,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96215,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "No! You are going to know."
                },
                {
                    "id": 218314,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Jangan sekali-kali (bersikap demikian)! Kamu akan mengetahui kelak (akibatnya yang buruk semasa hendak mati)!"
                },
                {
                    "id": 1097148,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "(তোমরা যে ভুল ধারণায় ডুবে আছো তা) মোটেই ঠিক নয়, শীঘ্রই তোমরা জানতে পারবে,"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 6172,
            "verse_number": 4,
            "verse_key": "102:4",
            "hizb_number": 60,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
            "ruku_number": 546,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "ثُمَّ كَلَّا سَوْفَ تَعْلَمُونَ",
            "page_number": 600,
            "juz_number": 30,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96217,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "Then, no! You are going to know."
                },
                {
                    "id": 214708,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Sekali lagi (diingatkan): jangan sekali-kali (kamu bersikap demikian)! Kamu akan mengetahui kelak akibatnya yang buruk pada hari kiamat)!"
                },
                {
                    "id": 1097149,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "আবার বলি, মোটেই ঠিক নয়, শীঘ্রই তোমরা জানতে পারবে।"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 6173,
            "verse_number": 5,
            "verse_key": "102:5",
            "hizb_number": 60,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
            "ruku_number": 546,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "كَلَّا لَوْ تَعْلَمُونَ عِلْمَ ٱلْيَقِينِ",
            "page_number": 600,
            "juz_number": 30,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96219,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "No! If you only knew with knowledge of certainty...<sup foot_note=197809>1</sup>"
                },
                {
                    "id": 219323,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Demi sesungguhnya! Kalaulah kamu mengetahui - (apa yang kamu akan hadapi) - dengan pengetahuan yang yakin, (tentulah kamu akan mengerjakan perkara-perkara yang menjadi bekalan kamu untuk hari akhirat)."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1097150,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "কক্ষনো না, তোমরা যদি নিশ্চিত জ্ঞানের ভিত্তিতে জানতে! (তাহলে সাবধান হয়ে যেতে)"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 6174,
            "verse_number": 6,
            "verse_key": "102:6",
            "hizb_number": 60,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
            "ruku_number": 546,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "لَتَرَوُنَّ ٱلْجَحِيمَ",
            "page_number": 600,
            "juz_number": 30,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96221,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "You will surely see the Hellfire."
                },
                {
                    "id": 214648,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "(Ingatlah) demi sesungguhnya! - Kamu akan melihat neraka yang marak menjulang."
                },
                {
                    "id": 1097151,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "তোমরা অবশ্য অবশ্যই জাহান্নাম দেখতে পাবে,"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 6175,
            "verse_number": 7,
            "verse_key": "102:7",
            "hizb_number": 60,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
            "ruku_number": 546,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "ثُمَّ لَتَرَوُنَّهَا عَيْنَ ٱلْيَقِينِ",
            "page_number": 600,
            "juz_number": 30,
            "translations": [
                {
                    "id": 96223,
                    "resource_id": 20,
                    "text": "Then you will surely see it with the eye of certainty.<sup foot_note=197810>1</sup>"
                },
                {
                    "id": 220847,
                    "resource_id": 39,
                    "text": "Selepas itu - demi sesungguhnya! - kamu (wahai orang-orang yang derhaka) akan melihatnya dengan penglihatan yang yakin (semasa kamu dilemparkan ke dalamnya)!"
                },
                {
                    "id": 1097152,
                    "resource_id": 161,
                    "text": "আবার বলি, তোমরা তা অবশ্য অবশ্যই দিব্য দৃষ্টিতে দেখতে পাবে,"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": 6176,
            "verse_number": 8,
            "verse_key": "102:8",
            "hizb_number": 60,
            "rub_el_hizb_number": 240,
            "ruku_number": 546,
            "manzil_number": 7,
            "sajdah_number": null,
            "text_uthmani": "ثُمَّ لَتُسْـَٔلُنَّ يَوْمَئِذٍ عَنِ ٱلنَّعِيمِ",
            "page_number": 600,
            "juz_number": 30,
